<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Sunnyside</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Once home to Canadian Pacific Railway and the Eau Clare Saw Mill workers, Sunnyside now attracts Urban Professionals and their families, who are drawn to the area for its quiet and friendly atmosphere located within walking distance to shops, restaurants, transportation and the downtown Calgary core.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The area is home to various unique shops, including Kensington Art Supply (appropriate for the close proximity to SAIT and ACAD) Urban Barn and The Rocket, a clothing chain exclusive to Calgary.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">A Safeway is located in north Kensington, making grocery shopping an easy trip for Sunnyside residents.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Food and entertainment is also available, from evening/nightlife places like Kensington Pub to more relaxed places like Oolong Tea House.</p>

        </div>
